== 数词 Numerals

*数词*（Numeral）就是表示数目和次序的词。

在英语中，数词分为基数词（cardinal numbers）和序数词（ordinal numbers）两类。

=== 基数词 Cardinal Numbers

表示确定的数目，多放在事物前面。例如：一、十、千、亿等。数词是表示数目的多少和顺序的先后的词。

基本的基数词有
#three-line-table[
  | 1-10 | $10+n$ | $n times 10$ | $10^n$ |
  | --- | --- | --- | --- |
  | 1 one | 11 eleven | 10 ten | 100 a hundred |
  | 2 two | 12 twelve | 20 twenty | 1,000 a thousand |
  | 3 three | 13 thirteen | 30 thirty | 1,000,000 a million |
  | 4 four | 14 fourteen | 40 forty | 1,000,000,000 a billion |
  | 5 five | 15 fifteen | 50 fifty | 1,000,000,000,000 a trillion |
  | 6 six | 16 sixteen | 60 sixty | \ |
  | 7 seven | 17 seventeen | 70 seventy | \ |
  | 8 eight | 18 eighteen | 80 eighty | \ |
  | 9 nine | 19 nineteen | 90 ninety | \ |
]
- 零：zero / nought / O（电话号码中读作 “oh”）

其他的基数词由此构成：
- 几十几：几十-几
  - 21 twenty-one、22 twenty-two、23 twenty-three
- 几百几十几：几百 and 几十几
  - 233 two hundred and thirty-three
- 大于一千的数：三位截断（数词用单数）
  - 1,234 one thousand, two hundred and thirty-four
  - 11,990 eleven thousand, nine hundred and ninety
  - 12,345,678 twelve million, three hundred and forty-five thousand, six hundred and seventy-eight

用法：
- 作主语、宾语、表语等。
  - Five is an odd number.
  - We are altogether fifteen.
- 作定语，修饰名词。
  - I have three books.
- 复数形式表示泛指
  - hundreds of
    - three hundred students
    - hundreds of people
  - thousands of ...
  - millions of ...

=== 序数词 Ordinal Numbers

表示计算或排行事物的次序。例如：第一、初二等。

#three-line-table[
  | 1-10 | $10+n$ | $n times 10$ |
  | --- | --- | --- |
  | 1st first | 11th eleventh | 10th tenth |
  | 2nd second | 12th twelfth | 20th twentieth |
  | 3rd third | 13th thirteenth | 30th thirtieth |
  | 4th fourth | 14th fourteenth | 40th fortieth |
  | 5th fifth | 15th fifteenth | 50th fiftieth |
  | 6th sixth | 16th sixteenth | 60th sixtieth |
  | 7th seventh | 17th seventeenth | 70th seventieth |
  | 8th eighth | 18th eighteenth | 80th eightieth |
  | 9th ninth | 19th nineteenth | 90th ninetieth |
]
- 除了1,2,3都是+th
- -ty要变y为i再+th

用法：
- 作定语，必须加定冠词the（或者物主代词）
  - the first book
  - their second son
- 不加定冠词表示“再一” = another one
  - We'll have to do it a second time.

要点：
- 编号
  - the 序数词 名词 = 名词 基数词
    - the first chapter = chapter one
- 年份
  - 分成两个两位数读
    - 1990 = nineteen ninety
- 日期
  - 日期是序数词
    - 1.1 = January 1st = January (the) first = the first of January
- 时刻
  - 整点 o'clock
    - 8:00 = eight o'clock
  - 半点 half past/thirty
    - 8:30 = eight thirty = half past eight
  - 十五
    - 8:15 = eight fifteen = a quarter past eight
  - 四十五
    - 8:45 = eight forty-five = a quarter to nine
  - 半之前
    - 8:12 = eight twelve = twelve past eight
  - 半之后
    - 8:54 = eight fifty-four = six to nine

=== 倍数

表示倍数，多用“倍”字表示。例如：十倍等。

- once
- twice
- n times

=== 分数

- 分数
  $
    a/b
  $
  读成：a over b或者a基数词b序数词，注意序数词的单复数

  - $1/4$: one-fourth
  - $3/4$: three-fourths
  - $2 3/5$: two and three-fifths

  还有特殊
  - $1/2$: half
  - $3/2$: three-halves
  - $1/4$: quarter
  - $2 3/4$: two and three-quarters

- 小数
  - 小数点后的数字顺次朗读
  - $3.1415$: three point one four one five
- 百分数
  - per cent
  - $25%$: twenty-five per cent
